OL,3,CMan, 57, charged with murder of 28-
OL,4,Cyear-old
OL,6,FA 57-year-old Plymouth man has
OL,7,Fappeared in court today (Friday 8 May)
OL,8,Fcharged with murder.
OL,10,FMark Carpenter, of Embankment Road, is
OL,11,Faccused of murdering 28-year-old Harry
OL,12,FJackson.
OL,14,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,15,Fproperty in Embankment Road on Monday
OL,16,Fevening and Mr Jackson was found with
OL,17,Fserious injuries but later died at the
OL,18,Fscene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
