OL,3,CMan, 57, charged with murder of 28-
OL,4,Cyear-old
OL,6,FCarpenter appeared at Plymouth
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court and confirmed his
OL,8,Fname, date of birth and address during
OL,9,Fa two-minute remand hearing.
OL,11,FA District Judge said the issue of
OL,12,Fbail cannot be dealt with by the
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court and the 57-year-old
OL,14,Fwas remanded in custody to sppear
OL,15,Fbefore a judge at Plymouth Crown Court
OL,16,Fon Monday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
