OL,3,CMan, 57, charged with murder of 28-
OL,4,Cyear-old
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Jo Rotchell, from
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police's Major
OL,8,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "This
OL,9,Fis a tragic incident in which a person
OL,10,Fhas lost their life.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with the family
OL,13,Fand friends of Harry at this
OL,14,Fincredibly difficult time. We will
OL,15,Fcontinue to support those affected."
